        <Summary>A python library for arbitrary-precision floating-point arithmetic</Summary>
        <Description>Mpmath implements a large set of mathematical functions and provides utilities for arbitrary-precision numerical differentiation, integration, root-finding, interval arithmetic, and other tasks. It supports unlimited exponent sizes, has full support for complex numbers, and is faster than Python's standard decimal library.</Description>
